gather_item

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
gather_item -  This method attempts to gather some items in the environment of the specified player.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
object * gather_item(string word,
object player)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^word%^RESET%^ - the item to try and gather
%^BOLD%^player%^RESET%^ - the player doing the gathering
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
an array of gathered objects.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/gathering.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method attempts to gather some items in the environment of
the specified player.
.EP

